These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, swisher, dunhill, old-henry
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, fisherman, pilot, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, funk, hip-hop, house
4 different pets are kept: hamster, frog, hedgehog, rat
 1. the fan house is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
 3. the dannemann-smoker is not the owner of the frog##6
 4. the fan hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan funk##3
 5. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the fan house##5
 6. the security-guard is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
 7. the fan disco is the dannemann-smoker##1
 8. the dannemann-smoker is between the owner of the hedgehog and the architect##2
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
10. the owner of the rat is not the fisherman##6
11. the swisher-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan house is in an odd position##4
13. the dunhill-smoker is the fan house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | dunhill     | dannemann      | old-henry      | swisher    |
| Food          | architect    | fisherman | security-guard | pilot     |
| Music-Genre   | house    | disco     | hip-hop    | funk     |
| Nationality   | rat | hamster | hedgehog    | frog |

