 1. the person who likes emerald is the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the ranch-style house and the person watching epic movies##2
 7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 8. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the victorian house##1
10. the person who likes lilac is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
11. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
12. the ranch-style house is not the person who likes emerald##6
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
14. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the palace house##3

