12. the farmhouse house is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person traveling to hannover##2
13. the person traveling to hannover is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | san-francisco | hannover     | marseilles    | london |
| Music-Genre   | colonial | tower       | farmhouse | palace    |
| Pet           | goat    | chinchilla | mouse      | guinea-pig |
| Transport     | november     | march     | february     | july |

