.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-18::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, bridge, billiard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, soul, d&b, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, colombian, french
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, satire, thriller, scientific
 1. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching satire movies and the australian##2
 3. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
 4. the person watching scientific movies is the fan soul##1
 5. the french is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 6. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
 7. the person playing monopoly is not the colombian##6
 8. the person playing bridge is the french##1
 9. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
10. the person playing canasta is on the left of the fan reggae##1
11. the person watching satire movies is the fan reggae##1
12. the fan d&b is on the left of the fan reggae##1
13. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

