.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, salsa, disco, punk
House: palace, tower, townhouse, farmhouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cricket, sailing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, tea, cola
 1. the person drinking cola is not the tower house##6
 2. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
 4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
 5. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the fan disco##5
 7. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 9. the tower house is on the far left or far right##3
10. the palace house is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
13. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the fan salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
