.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-20::.
City: hamburg, rome, berlin, new-york
4 different games are played: poker, monopoly, domino, backgammon
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, blue, brown, chestnut
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, skateboard, snowmobile
 1. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
 2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is not the person playing poker##6
 4. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
 7. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 9. the person who likes brown is not the person traveling to hamburg##6
10. the person traveling to hamburg is not the person driving the skateboard##6
11. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | new-york | rome  | berlin     | hamburg     |
| Movie-Genre   | domino   | monopoly      | poker   | backgammon     |
| Nationality   | blue  | orange   | brown  | chestnut       |
| Transport     | scooter   | helicopter | skateboard | snowmobile |

 